item.title: About
item.description: This is my basic Honours blog. It was based off of the default blogdown template. The original About text is listed below. This is a “hello world” example website for the blogdown package. The theme was forked from @jrutheiser/hugo-lithium-theme and modified by Yihui Xie.

item.title: Chow’s Test
item.description: Chow’s test Here we will be using Chow’s test to test for structural breaks in the flutracking data. Specifically, we’ll be testing the % of unvaccinated respondents reporting influenza-like illness (ILI) symptoms using the strucchange package in R. Unvaccinated Repsondents Data ## Adding missing grouping variables: `variable`
